Version 43.beta
~~~~~~~~~~~~

Port to Gtk4/Adwaita, taking advantage of Adwaita's recolouring
features and thus removing our dependency on sassc. We now
require that Vte is be built with gtk4 support.

Nautilus Plug-in has been moved upstream.

Simon McVittie improved our handeling of custom shells/commands,
fixing several bugs and providing a more predictable experience.

Colin Kinloch provided fixes for drag-n-drop, with local URIs now
being converted to regular fileystem paths.

Assorted other fixes were contributed, including detection of man
page links, keyboard shortcuts, clipboard oddities, building with
clang, and assorted ancillary data updates.

